  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/47072ea0b265414cd551e94c1176bbd4.poster.avif?t=1729979087\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/47072ea0b265414cd551e94c1176bbd4.webm?t=1729979087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/47072ea0b265414cd551e94c1176bbd4.mp4?t=1729979087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Dive into the retro horror of <strong>Don't Wake Up The Dead</strong>, an intense survival game that will test your nerves. After a funeral urn was accidentally opened in an old attic, a malevolent spirit has been unleashed. Your mission? Seal the urn before it's too late.<br><br>But beware, your only weapon is a <strong>flashlight that quickly weakens</strong>, and one wrong move could wake the ghost! The key to survival: <strong>make no noise !</strong> <strong>The faster you move, the more noise you make</strong>, and the closer you are to disaster. Every step counts, especially in this house where doors lock randomly with each new game, turning the house into a different maze every time you play.<br><br>For an extra layer of competition, a<strong> point system</strong> and <strong>bonus rewards</strong> have been added. Race against your friends to see who can seal the ghost fastest while managing noise levels and earning extra points by completing hidden challenges. <strong>Strategic gameplay</strong> and smart use of bonuses can make all the difference in who comes out on top!  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/4a12775bdb7e0371fbb789ffb82043f9.poster.avif?t=1729979087\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/4a12775bdb7e0371fbb789ffb82043f9.webm?t=1729979087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/4a12775bdb7e0371fbb789ffb82043f9.mp4?t=1729979087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Key Features:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/ec5acf10806e74b205ee5fe847cb1e38.webp?t=1729979087\" width=20 height=20 /></span>  <strong>Solo survival</strong> or <strong>multiplayer</strong> (<strong>turn-based</strong>) to share the terror with friends<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/c9727c7299499ce21e627f114323bdd3.webp?t=1729979087\" width=20 height=20 /></span>  A <strong>flashlight</strong> as your only ally, but it <strong>weakens quickly</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/85038dcb9d4172f8ae3f327db4ff9cb0.webp?t=1729979087\" width=20 height=20 /></span>  A delicate balance between <strong>speed</strong> and <strong>stealth: move fast, but not too loud !</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/58a9d27b6dbf9b49654abc1419c94e74.webp?t=1729979087\" width=20 height=20 /></span>   <strong>Doors lock randomly</strong> with each new game, creating a <strong>unique maze</strong> each time<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/7d8c6b3e42da06ce2337a1368cda6b5f.webp?t=1729979087\" width=20 height=20 /></span><strong>  Point and bonus</strong> system to increase competition with rewards for fast, stealthy, and <strong>strategic gameplay</strong>  <br><br>Can you seal the urn before the ghost wakes... forever?",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/47072ea0b265414cd551e94c1176bbd4.poster.avif?t=1729979087\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/47072ea0b265414cd551e94c1176bbd4.webm?t=1729979087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/47072ea0b265414cd551e94c1176bbd4.mp4?t=1729979087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Dive into the retro horror of <strong>Don't Wake Up The Dead</strong>, an intense survival game that will test your nerves. After a funeral urn was accidentally opened in an old attic, a malevolent spirit has been unleashed. Your mission? Seal the urn before it's too late.<br><br>But beware, your only weapon is a <strong>flashlight that quickly weakens</strong>, and one wrong move could wake the ghost! The key to survival: <strong>make no noise !</strong> <strong>The faster you move, the more noise you make</strong>, and the closer you are to disaster. Every step counts, especially in this house where doors lock randomly with each new game, turning the house into a different maze every time you play.<br><br>For an extra layer of competition, a<strong> point system</strong> and <strong>bonus rewards</strong> have been added. Race against your friends to see who can seal the ghost fastest while managing noise levels and earning extra points by completing hidden challenges. <strong>Strategic gameplay</strong> and smart use of bonuses can make all the difference in who comes out on top!  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217650/extras/4a12775bdb7e0371fbb789ffb82043f9.poster.avif?t=1729979087\" width